                        "requirement": "The giant mosquito has a creature grabbed or restrained",
                        "effect": "The giant mosquito uses its proboscis to drain blood from the grabbed or restrained creature. This deals 3d6 piercing damage (DC 24 basic Fortitude save), and the giant mosquito gains temporary Hit Points equal to the damage dealt that last 1 minute. A creature that takes any damage from having its blood drained by a giant mosquito is drained 1 until it receives any kind or amount of healing."
                    }
